msgid "# Long-Sequence Context Parallel (Qwen3-235B-A22B)"
msgstr "# 长序列上下文并行（Qwen3-235B-A22B）"

msgid "## Getting Started"
msgstr "## 快速开始"

msgid ""
"vLLM-Ascend now supports long-sequence context parallel. This guide takes "
"one-by-one steps to verify these features with constrained resources."
msgstr "vLLM-Ascend 现已支持长序列上下文并行。本指南将逐步指导您在有限资源下验证这些功能。"

msgid ""
"Using the `Qwen3-235B-A22B-w8a8` (Quantized version) model as an example, "
"use 1 Atlas 800 A3 (64G × 16) server to deploy the single node \"pd co-"
"locate\" architecture."
msgstr ""
"以 `Qwen3-235B-A22B-w8a8`（量化版本）模型为例，使用 1 台 Atlas 800 A3（64G × 16）服务器部署单节点“PD "
"共部署”架构。"

msgid "## Environment Preparation"
msgstr "## 环境准备"

msgid "### Model Weight"
msgstr "### 模型权重"

msgid ""
"- `Qwen3-235B-A22B-w8a8` (Quantized version): requires 1 Atlas 800 A3 (64G ×"
" 16) node. [Download model weight](https://modelscope.cn/models/vllm-"
"ascend/Qwen3-235B-A22B-W8A8)"
msgstr ""
"- `Qwen3-235B-A22B-w8a8`（量化版本）：需要 1 个 Atlas 800 A3（64G × "
"16）节点。[下载模型权重](https://modelscope.cn/models/vllm-"
"ascend/Qwen3-235B-A22B-W8A8)"

msgid ""
"It is recommended to download the model weight to the shared directory of "
"multiple nodes, such as `/root/.cache/`"
msgstr "建议将模型权重下载到多节点共享目录，例如 `/root/.cache/`"

msgid "### Run with Docker"
msgstr "### 使用 Docker 运行"

msgid "Start a Docker container on each node."
msgstr "在每个节点上启动一个 Docker 容器。"

msgid "## Deployment"
msgstr "## 部署"

msgid "### Single-node Deployment"
msgstr "### 单节点部署"

msgid ""
"`Qwen3-235B-A22B-w8a8` can be deployed on 1 Atlas 800 A3（64G*16）.\n"
"Quantized version needs to start with parameter `--quantization ascend`."
msgstr ""
"`Qwen3-235B-A22B-w8a8` 可部署在 1 台 Atlas 800 A3（64G*16）上。\n"
"量化版本需要添加参数 `--quantization ascend` 启动。"

msgid "Run the following script to execute online 128k inference."
msgstr "运行以下脚本执行在线 128k 推理。"

msgid ""
"- for vllm version below `v0.12.0` use parameter: `--rope_scaling '{\"rope_type\":\"yarn\",\"factor\":4,\"original_max_position_embeddings\":32768}' \\`\n"
"- for vllm version `v0.12.0` use parameter: `--hf-overrides '{\"rope_parameters\": {\"rope_type\":\"yarn\",\"rope_theta\":1000000,\"factor\":4,\"original_max_position_embeddings\":32768}}' \\`"
msgstr ""
"- 对于 `v0.12.0` 以下版本的 vllm，使用参数：`--rope_scaling '{\"rope_type\":\"yarn\",\"factor\":4,\"original_max_position_embeddings\":32768}' \\`\n"
"- 对于 `v0.12.0` 版本的 vllm，使用参数：`--hf-overrides '{\"rope_parameters\": {\"rope_type\":\"yarn\",\"rope_theta\":1000000,\"factor\":4,\"original_max_position_embeddings\":32768}}' \\`"

msgid "The parameters are explained as follows:"
msgstr "参数说明如下："

msgid ""
"- `--tensor-parallel-size` 8 are common settings for tensor parallelism (TP) sizes.\n"
"- `--prefill-context-parallel-size` 2 are common settings for prefill context parallelism (PCP) sizes.\n"
"- `--decode-context-parallel-size` 2 are common settings for decode context parallelism (DCP) sizes.\n"
"- `--max-model-len` represents the context length, which is the maximum value of the input plus output for a single request.\n"
"- `--max-num-seqs` indicates the maximum number of requests that each DP group is allowed to process. If the number of requests sent to the service exceeds this limit, the excess requests will remain in a waiting state and will not be scheduled. Note that the time spent in the waiting state is also counted in metrics such as TTFT and TPOT. Therefore, when testing performance, it is generally recommended that `--max-num-seqs` * `--data-parallel-size` >= the actual total concurrency.\n"
"- `--max-num-batched-tokens` represents the maximum number of tokens that the model can process in a single step. Currently, vLLM v1 scheduling enables ChunkPrefill/SplitFuse by default, which means:\n"
"    - (1) If the input length of a request is greater than `--max-num-batched-tokens`, it will be divided into multiple rounds of computation according to `--max-num-batched-tokens`;\n"
"    - (2) Decode requests are prioritized for scheduling, and prefill requests are scheduled only if there is available capacity.\n"
"    - Generally, if `--max-num-batched-tokens` is set to a larger value, the overall latency will be lower, but the pressure on GPU memory (activation value usage) will be greater.\n"
"- `--gpu-memory-utilization` represents the proportion of HBM that vLLM will use for actual inference. Its essential function is to calculate the available kv_cache size. During the warm-up phase (referred to as profile run in vLLM), vLLM records the peak GPU memory usage during an inference process with an input size of `--max-num-batched-tokens`. The available kv_cache size is then calculated as: `--gpu-memory-utilization` * HBM size - peak GPU memory usage. Therefore, the larger the value of `--gpu-memory-utilization`, the more kv_cache can be used. However, since the GPU memory usage during the warm-up phase may differ from that during actual inference (e.g., due to uneven EP load), setting `--gpu-memory-utilization` too high may lead to OOM (Out of Memory) issues during actual inference. The default value is `0.9`.\n"
"- `--enable-expert-parallel` indicates that EP is enabled. Note that vLLM does not support a mixed approach of EP and TP; that is, MoE can either use pure EP or pure TP.\n"
"- `--no-enable-prefix-caching` indicates that prefix caching is disabled. To enable it, remove this option.\n"
"- `--quantization` \"ascend\" indicates that quantization is used. To disable quantization, remove this option.\n"
"- `--compilation-config` contains configurations related to the aclgraph graph mode. The most significant configurations are \"cudagraph_mode\" and \"cudagraph_capture_sizes\", which have the following meanings:\n"
"\"cudagraph_mode\": represents the specific graph mode. Currently, \"PIECEWISE\" and \"FULL_DECODE_ONLY\" are supported. The graph mode is mainly used to reduce the cost of operator dispatch. Currently, \"FULL_DECODE_ONLY\" is recommended.\n"
"- \"cudagraph_capture_sizes\": represents different levels of graph modes. The default value is [1, 2, 4, 8, 16, 24, 32, 40,..., `--max-num-seqs`]. In the graph mode, the input for graphs at different levels is fixed, and inputs between levels are automatically padded to the next level. Currently, the default setting is recommended. Only in some scenarios is it necessary to set this separately to achieve optimal performance.\n"
"- `export VLLM_ASCEND_ENABLE_FLASHCOMM1=1` indicates that Flashcomm1 optimization is enabled. Currently, this optimization is only supported for MoE in scenarios where tp_size > 1."
msgstr ""
"- `--tensor-parallel-size` 8 是张量并行（TP）大小的常见设置。\n"
"- `--prefill-context-parallel-size` 2 是预填充上下文并行（PCP）大小的常见设置。\n"
"- `--decode-context-parallel-size` 2 是解码上下文并行（DCP）大小的常见设置。\n"
"- `--max-model-len` 表示上下文长度，即单个请求输入加输出的最大值。\n"
"- `--max-num-seqs` 表示每个 DP 组允许处理的最大请求数。如果发送到服务的请求数超过此限制，多余的请求将保持等待状态，不会被调度。注意，等待状态所花费的时间也会计入 TTFT 和 TPOT 等指标。因此，在测试性能时，通常建议 `--max-num-seqs` * `--data-parallel-size` >= 实际总并发数。\n"
"- `--max-num-batched-tokens` 表示模型单步可处理的最大 token 数。目前，vLLM v1 调度默认启用 ChunkPrefill/SplitFuse，这意味着：\n"
"    - (1) 如果某个请求的输入长度大于 `--max-num-batched-tokens`，则会根据 `--max-num-batched-tokens` 将其拆分为多轮计算；\n"
"    - (2) 优先调度解码请求，仅在有空闲容量时才调度预填充请求。\n"
"    - 通常，如果 `--max-num-batched-tokens` 设置得较大，整体延迟会更低，但对 GPU 内存（激活值使用）的压力会更大。\n"
"- `--gpu-memory-utilization` 表示 vLLM 将用于实际推理的 HBM 比例。其本质功能是计算可用的 kv_cache 大小。在预热阶段（vLLM 中称为 profile run），vLLM 会记录一次输入大小为 `--max-num-batched-tokens` 的推理过程中的峰值 GPU 内存使用量。然后，可用的 kv_cache 大小计算如下：`--gpu-memory-utilization` * HBM 大小 - 峰值 GPU 内存使用量。因此，`--gpu-memory-utilization` 的值越大，可用的 kv_cache 就越多。但是，由于预热阶段的 GPU 内存使用量可能与实际推理时不同（例如，由于 EP 负载不均），将 `--gpu-memory-utilization` 设置得过高可能会导致实际推理时出现 OOM（内存不足）问题。默认值为 `0.9`。\n"
"- `--enable-expert-parallel` 表示启用 EP。注意，vLLM 不支持 EP 和 TP 的混合方式；也就是说，MoE 要么使用纯 EP，要么使用纯 TP。\n"
"- `--no-enable-prefix-caching` 表示禁用前缀缓存。要启用它，请移除该选项。\n"
"- `--quantization` \"ascend\" 表示使用量化。要禁用量化，请移除该选项。\n"
"- `--compilation-config` 包含与 aclgraph 图模式相关的配置。其中最重要的配置是 \"cudagraph_mode\" 和 \"cudagraph_capture_sizes\"，其含义如下：\n"
"\"cudagraph_mode\"：表示具体的图模式。目前支持 \"PIECEWISE\" 和 \"FULL_DECODE_ONLY\"。图模式主要用于降低算子调度的开销。目前推荐使用 \"FULL_DECODE_ONLY\"。\n"
"- \"cudagraph_capture_sizes\"：表示不同级别的图模式。默认值为 [1, 2, 4, 8, 16, 24, 32, 40,..., `--max-num-seqs`]。在图模式下，不同级别图的输入是固定的，级别之间的输入会自动填充到下一级别。目前建议使用默认设置。仅在部分场景下需要单独设置以达到最佳性能。\n"
"- `export VLLM_ASCEND_ENABLE_FLASHCOMM1=1` 表示启用 Flashcomm1 优化。目前，该优化仅在 tp_size > 1 的 MoE 场景中支持。"

msgid "**Notice:**"
msgstr "**注意：**"

msgid ""
"- tp_size needs to be divisible by dcp_size\n"
"- decode context parallel size must be less than or equal to max_dcp_size, where max_dcp_size = tensor_parallel_size // total_num_kv_heads."
msgstr ""
"- tp_size 必须能被 dcp_size 整除\n"
"- 解码上下文并行大小必须小于或等于 max_dcp_size，其中 max_dcp_size = tensor_parallel_size // total_num_kv_heads。"

